title: What should I do with my gemstone?
body:
I have Omega Squad Teemo, and enough essence, but I wasn't sure what to do.
I also have Gatekeeper Galio, but not Galio, and I have Blood Moon Shen and Warden Jax.
I was wondering what I should do? Should I wait for more skins? I have 9 chests and 0 keys and 0 fragments

replies.body: I also don't know whether I like teemo enough yet.
